<P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설] 겉넓이에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000143" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1143"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2(ab+bc+ca)=236</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, 모서리 합에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000144" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1144"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>4(a+b+c)+6=82</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000145" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1145"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>ab+bc+ca=118, a+b+c=19</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000146" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1146"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="27922" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>overline {HI}^{2} = (a-1)^{2}+(b-1)^{2}+(c-1)^{2} = a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2}-2(a+b+c)+3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이며, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000147" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1147"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a^{2}+b^{2}+c^{2} = 19^{2}-2(118)=125</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 대입하면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000148" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1148"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11092" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>overline {HI}^{2} = 125-38+3=90</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE><CHAR> 그림1]과 같이 모든 모서리의 길이가 1보다 큰 직육면체 모양의 나무토막 ABCD-EFGH가 있다. 이 나무토막의 한 모퉁이에서 한 모서리의 길이가 1인 정육면체 모양의 나무토막을 잘라내어 버리고 [그림2]와 같은 입체도형을 만들었다. [그림2]의 입체도형의 겉넓이는 236이고, 모든 모서리의 길이의 합은 82일 때, 잘라낸 부분 중 나무토막 안쪽에 생긴 꼭짓점 I에 대하여 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000149" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1149"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3612" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>overline {HI}^{2}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 값은?</CHAR></TEXT></P>
